Moore, 1888
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Hu, S. J. &amp; Cotton, A. M. &amp; Condamine, F. L. &amp; Duan, K. &amp; Wang, R. J. &amp; Hsu, Y. F. &amp; Zhang, X. &amp; Cao, J." box="[959,1126,189,215]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" pagination="401 - 446" refId="ref5941" refString="Hu, S. J., Cotton, A. M., Condamine, F. L., Duan, K., Wang, R. J., Hsu, Y. F., Zhang, X. &amp; Cao, J. (2018) Revision of Pazala Moore, 1888: The Graphium (Pazala) mandarinus (Oberthur, 1879) Group, with treatments of known taxa and descriptions of new species and new subspecies (Lepidoptera: Papilionidae). Zootaxa, 4441 (3), 401 - 446. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4441.3.1" type="journal article" year="2018">
Hu 
<emphasis box="[1003,1053,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">et al</emphasis>
. 2018
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Hu, S. J. &amp; Condamine, F. L. &amp; Monastyrskii, A. L. &amp; Cotton, A. M." box="[1138,1198,189,215]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" pagination="286 - 300" refId="ref5868" refString="Hu, S. J., Condamine, F. L., Monastyrskii, A. L. &amp; Cotton, A. M. (2019) A new species of the Graphium (Pazala) mandarinus Group from Central Vietnam (Lepidoptera: Papilionidae). Zootaxa, 4554 (1), 286 - 300. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4554.1.10" type="journal article" year="2019">2019</bibRefCitation>
), 
<emphasis box="[1218,1353,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Devyatkinia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Monastyrskii, A. L. &amp; Uemura, Y." pageId="11" pageNumber="228" pagination="131 - 137" refId="ref6319" refString="Monastyrskii, A. L. &amp; Uemura, Y. (2016) Unique wood nymphs from China and Vietnam: Devyatkinia singularis gen. et spec. nov. Atalanta, 47 (1 / 2), 131 - 137." type="journal article" year="2016">Monastyrskii &amp; Uémura, 2016</bibRefCitation>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Hubner, 1819" authorityName="Hubner" authorityYear="1819" box="[447,671,225,251]" class="Insecta" family="Nymphalidae" genus="Lethe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[447,509,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Lethe</emphasis>
Hübner, 1819
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Lang, S. Y. &amp; Monastyrskii, A. L." box="[686,999,225,252]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" pagination="453 - 462" refId="ref6139" refString="Lang, S. Y. &amp; Monastyrskii, A. L. (2016) Description of two new species of the Lethe manzorum - group (Lepidoptera, Nymphalidae, Satyrinae) from China. Zootaxa, 4103 (5), 453 - 462. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4103.5.3" type="journal article" year="2016">Lang &amp; Monastyrskii 2016</bibRefCitation>
), 
<taxonomicName authority="Hubner, 1818" authorityName="Hubner" authorityYear="1818" box="[1019,1271,225,251]" class="Insecta" family="Nymphalidae" genus="Ypthima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1019,1110,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="228">Ypthima</emphasis>
Hübner, 1818
</taxonomicName>
(Monastyrskii &amp; Holoway 2013), etc. Sometimes these disjunctions may be filled with the populations of closely related species, showing the characters of vicariance, the existence of refugiums and the speciation processes occurred in this area.
</paragraph>
